data.description: The view from your beautiful kitchen, breakfast nook & covered deck is amazing! This well kept home has recently had many upgrades including new kitchen cabinets, flooring & granite countertops. The roof was replaced around 2017. This perfect hobby farm has something for everyone. Small pasture with loafing shed, large shop with concrete floors & half bath, gazebo & plenty of parking. Located just minutes from town, it has a great well & the low taxes help with monthly expenses. Not a drive by!
